=== Description ===
PHP Retweeter will let you tweet, search for tweets, retweet found tweets,
follow people that mention you, and more!

=== Requirements ===
Abraham Williams' OAuth library
http://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth/tree/master/twitteroauth/

Place these files in a folder called 'twitteroauth'.

=== Usage ===
Check example.php to find out about some of the functions you can call
to use the Retweeter class. Check php_retweeter.php for all of the
functions you can use.

=== Change Log ===
2010/11/18, v1.1: Added a some functions to call the API directly and to
lookup users.
